00:51:13.980 --> 00:51:16.720
persist twenty years after the wall.

00:51:16.720 --> 00:51:19.010
How are they created?

00:51:19.010 --> 00:51:23.160
Even something as simple as different brands
that you get in the supermarket create a sense

00:51:23.160 --> 00:51:29.900
of identity and so some East German brands
that went out of business after the fall of

00:51:29.900 --> 00:51:37.550
the wall have been reintroduced because there
was this "ostalgie" means East, nostalgia

00:51:37.550 --> 00:51:43.510
for these old brands and people felt this
loss of home because, you know, theyíve been

00:51:43.510 --> 00:51:45.670
so enmeshed in this completely different culture.

00:51:45.670 --> 00:51:46.670
So, yeah.

00:51:46.670 --> 00:51:48.730
&gt;&gt;male #1: I have one more comment.

00:51:48.730 --> 00:51:51.440
I happened to have seen three of these walls
